1. Install Python
bash
python --version

2. Install Flask
bash
pip install flask

3. Create Project Files
A. Create a folder for your project:
bash
mkdir number_guessing_web
cd number_guessing_web

B. Create app.py file:
bash
notepad app.py  # or use any code editor like VSCode

C. Create templates folder and HTML file:
bash
mkdir templates
notepad templates/index.html

4. Run the App
In the terminal (inside the project folder), run:

bash
python app.py
